@startuml
title UML State Machine Diagram - Graderate

[*] --> Waiting

state Waiting <<choice>>
Waiting : entry / waiting for start date
Waiting : do / check current date
Waiting : exit / start date arrived

Waiting --> Active : [Start date arrived]

state Active
Active : entry / rate is active
Active : do / check current date
Active : exit / end of validity period reached

Active --> Expired : [End of validity period reached]

state Expired
Expired : entry / rate is expired
Expired : do / check expiration date
Expired : exit / one year from expiration date

Expired --> Archived : [One year from expiration date]

state Archived
Archived : entry / rate is archived
Archived : do / remove or archive rate
Archived : exit / final state

Active --> Expired
Expired --> Archived
Archived --> [*]

@enduml
